                            <comment id="14462785" author="codex22" created="Sat, 16 Jun 2007 14:35:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It looks like a simple method in DefaultGroovyMethods.java is all that is needed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;public static boolean isCase(Number caseValue, Number switchValue) {&lt;br/&gt;
     return NumberMath.compareTo(caseValue, switchValue)==0;&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The attached patch contains this method and adds some tests to SwitchWithDifferentTypesTest.groovy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
